<Base title="About — SnapJar" description="About SnapJar: free, private, browser-based calculators and image tools, and how to contact us.">
  <header class="head"><div class="wrap"><p class="kicker">About</p><h1>About SnapJar</h1></div></header>
  <div class="content">
    <p>SnapJar is a growing collection of <b>free online tools that run entirely in your browser</b>. Calculators, image utilities and handy converters — with one firm rule: your data never leaves your device. Nothing you type or upload is sent to a server, because there is no server doing the work. It all happens locally, on your machine.</p>
    <h2>Why we built it</h2>
    <p>Most "free tool" sites are slow, cluttered with pop-ups, and quietly upload your files. We wanted the opposite: fast, clean, private tools that load instantly and just work — on any phone or computer, with no signup.</p>
    <h2>How we stay free</h2>
    <p>SnapJar is funded by unobtrusive advertising placed so it never gets in the way of using a tool. That lets us keep every tool free for everyone.</p>
    <h2>A note on our calculators</h2>
    <p>Our finance calculators are computational tools that show you the math for the numbers you enter. They are for general information only and are not financial advice. For decisions about your money, consult a qualified professional.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Suggestions or a tool you'd like to see? Email <b>sankettoraskar.business@gmail.com</b>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
